FRONTLINE ROADS v0.30.1 CONSTRUCTION BOUNDARIES AUDIT

Release: 0.30.1-construction-boundaries

ROOT CAUSE
- v0.28.3 added every active defense as a construction anchor.
- Each placed defense inherited a 170m or 100m propagation radius.
- Chaining facilities therefore bypassed physical player movement.

CORRECTION
- Build anchors: active major bases, active simple bases, current player position only.
- Facility-origin build anchors: removed from production code.
- Legacy out-of-zone facilities: retained but cannot propagate range.
- Manual removal: two-step confirmation, no resource refund.
- Removal clears matching enemy targetDefenseId and marks all enemy routes for recalculation.

